                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940430-107-off591 t17940430-107-cd592"></join>, and stealing therein two pieces of printed callico, each containing 28 yards, value 4l. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17940430-107-victim1084" type="victimName">
                           Anthony 
                           Rawlinson
                        <interp inst="t17940430-107-victim1084" type="surname" value="Rawlinson"></interp>
